ing%20a%20third-hand%20car%20to%20owning%20a%20fleet.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20past%2C%20he%20revealed%20how%20he%20stayed%20focused%20on%20his%20acting%20career%20amidst%20challenges.%20Meanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20professional%20front%2C%20he's%20gearing%20up%20for%20Kabir%20Khan's%20'Chandu%20Champion'%20and%20'Bhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBSE%20To%20Introduce%20Pilot%20For%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20For%20Classes%206%2C%209%2C%2011%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20is%20set%20to%20introduce%20a%20pilot%20of%20the%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20for%20classes%206%2C%209%2C%20and%2011%20from%20the%202024-25%20academic%20session.%20All%20affiliated%20schools%20have%20been%20invited%20by%20the%20board%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBSE%20developed%20and%20circulated%20draft%20NCrF%20implementation%20guidelines%2C%20discussed%20them%20in%20multiple%20workshops%2C%20and%20received%20approval%20from%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Education.%20To%20further%20test%2C%20refine%2C%20and%20assess%20their%20effectiveness%20in%20real-world%20contexts%2C%20a%20pilot%20implementation%20of%20these%20guidelines%20has%20been%20planned%20in%20schools%20affiliated%20to%20CBSE%20in%20classes%206%2C%209%2C%20and%2011%2C%20with%20effect%20from%20session%202024-2025%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20heads%20of%20all%20the%20institutions%20affiliated%20with%20CBSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrincipals%20of%20interested%20schools%20for%20this%20pilot%20programme%20are%20requested%20to%20share%20their%20contact%20details%20through%20this%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScBihps-Gy0pJynqJwxpy_FtCOW6vnXxfGiGvK0qdXse4UL9g%2Fviewform%5C%22%3E%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20earn%20credits%20through%20various%20activities%20such%20as%20classroom%20instruction%2C%20laboratory%20work%2C%20projects%2C%20sports%2C%20performing%20arts%2C%20NCC%2C%20social%20work%2C%20vocational%20education%2C%20and%20experiential%20learning%2C%20including%20relevant%20professional%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20government%20introduced%20the%20National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20aimed%20at%20integrating%20school%2C%20higher%2C%20and%20vocational%20education%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accrue%20credits%20from%20pre-primary%20to%20PhD%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20formulated%20draft%20guidelines%20to%20execute%20the%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20close%20the%20gap%20in%20achievement%20of%20learning%20outcomes%20by%20shifting%20the%20classroom%20education%20to%20competency%20and%20learning%20outcome-based%20education%20and%20learning.%20The%20assessment%20is%20thus%20mandatory%20for%20earning%20credits%20for%20all%20types%20of%20learning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20credits%20earned%20shall%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credit%20(ABC)%20of%20a%20student%20which%20will%20be%20linked%20with%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20and%20DigiLocker%20of%20the%20student%2C%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712755080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fildclon_school-students_625x300_17_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-to-introduce-pilot-for-national-credit-framework-for-classes-6-9-and-11-5413759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Credit%20Framework%20(NCrF)%20