le%22%3A%22Tissue%20Sample%20Moved%2037%20Km%20In%2020%20Min%2C%20Mid-Surgery%2C%20For%20Cancer%20Testing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research's%20(ICMR)%20trial%20run%2C%20a%20tissue%20sample%20was%20transported%20mid-surgery%20from%20a%20peripheral%20hospital%20in%20Karnataka%20for%20advanced%20pathological%20testing%20at%20a%20tertiary%20setting%20to%20decide%20if%20the%20resected%20tissue%20was%20cancerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20continuance%20with%20the%20national%20mission%20of%20expanding%20the%20drone%20ecosystem%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ICMR%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20trial%20run%20of%20transporting%20onco-pathological%20samples%20by%20drones%20under%20its%20i-Drone%20initiative%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20efficiently%20transported%20intraoperative%20surgical%20biospecimens%20surgically%20excised%20from%20the%20patient%20from%20Dr%20TMA%20Pai%20Hospital%2C%20Karkala%20to%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%2C%20Manipal%20Academy%20of%20Higher%20Education%20Manipal%20(tertiary%20care%20hospital)%2C%20covering%20a%20distance%20of%20approximately%2037%20km%20in%2015-20%20minutes%2C%20which%20takes%20around%2050-60%20minutes%20by%20road%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%2C%20the%20sample%20was%20promptly%20analysed%2C%20and%20the%20report%20was%20electronically%20conveyed%20back%20to%20the%20peripheral%20hospital.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20surgeon%20proceeded%20with%20the%20surgery%20based%20on%20the%20received%20report%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20trial%20run%20as%20part%20of%20a%20validation%20study%20has%20been%20undertaken%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20country%20by%20the%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20ICMR%2C%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%20(KMC)%20and%20Dr%20TMA%20PAI%20Rotary%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrones%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20agriculture%2C%20defence%2C%20disaster%20relief%20and%20healthcare%2C%20especially%20during%20emergency%20situations%20by%20enabling%20rapid%20delivery%20of%20vaccines%2C%20medications%2C%20and%20vital%20supplies%20to%20remote%20and%20inaccessible%20areas%2C%20the%20statement%20stated.%20The%20ICMR%20along%20with%20Kasturba%20Medical%20College%20is%20currently%20conducting%20a%20feasibility%20study%20in%20Manipal%2C%20Karnataka.%20The%20study%20aims%20to%20evaluate%20the%20potential%20use%20of%20aerial%20transportation%20systems%20(drones)%2C%20to%20transport%20items%20such%20as%20pathology%20samples%20from%20secondary%20healthcare%20facilities%20to%20tertiary-level%20hospitals%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E(1%2F2)%20Next%20milestone%20achieved%20in%20healthcare%20delivery%20via%20drone!%20Tissue%20sample%20transported%20mid-surgery%20from%20a%20peripheral%20hospital%20for%20Advanced%20pathological%20testing%20at%20tertiary%20setting%20for%20deciding%20if%20the%20resected%20tissue%20is%20cancerous%20or%20not.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoHFW_INDIA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MoHFW_INDIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhbFfjrPAD4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhbFfjrPAD4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ICMR%20(%40ICMRDELHI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICMRDELHI%2Fstatus%2F1777938278471319592%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransporting%20samples%20for%20intraoperative%20decision-making%20in%20remote%20areas%20hasn't%20been%20extensively%20explored%20or%20documented%20within%20the%20Indian%20context%20due%20to%20limited%20data%20on%20feasibility%2C%20utility%2C%20and%20cost-effectiveness.%20The%20ongoing%20research%20in%20Manipal%20aims%20to%20address%20this%20gap%20by%20documenting%20the%20procedures%20for%20quick%20transportation%20of%20intraoperative%20samples%20using%20drones%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20could%20potentially%20connect%20secondary%20care%20centres%20with%20limited%20resources%20to%20tertiary%20care%20facilities%20with%20advanced%20diagnostics%2C%20facilitating%20immediate%20access%20during%20surgical%20procedures.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20initiative%20could%20streamline%20complex%20surgeries%2C%20overcoming%20geographical%20barriers%20and%20improving%20access%20to%20specialized%20care%20in%20peripheral%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICMR%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20using%20drones%20for%20healthcare%20purposes%20and%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20delivery%20of%20medical%20supplies%2C%20vaccines%2C%20and%20medicines%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20blood%20bag%20delivery%20in%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20under%20its%20i-DRONE%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Dr%20Rajiv%20Bahl%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Department%20of%20Health%20Research%20(DHR)%20and%20Director%20General%2C%20ICMR%20emphasized%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20'i-DRONE'%20initiative%20was%20initially%20utilized%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20by%20ICMR%20for%20distributing%20vaccines%20to%20inaccessible%20areas.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20successfully%20conducted%20trials%20for%20delivering%20blood%20and%20blood-related%20products%2C%20which%20require%20low-temperature%20storage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20in%20another%20study%2C%20we%20transported%20medications%20and%20diagnostic%20samples%20to%20subzero%20temperature%20areas%20and%20challenging%20regions%20with%20altitudes%20exceeding%2012%2C000%20feet%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20In%20this%20ongoing%20study%2C%20our%20focus%20extends%20beyond%20delivering%20pathological%20specimens%3B%20we%20aim%20to%20enhance%20patient%20compliance%20and%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20tertiary%20care%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Atul%20Goel%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20(DGHS)%2C%20expressed%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20study%20holds%20significant%20relevance%20for%20the%20Indian%20context.%20The%20utilization%20of%20drones%20for%20delivering%20healthcare%20essentials%20during%20emergencies%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20save%20numerous%20lives.%20It%20can%20serve%20effectively%20in%20challenging%20geographical%20terrains%2C%20benefiting%20the%20Indian%20population%2C%20while%20also%20bolstering%20India's%20healthcare%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712754360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvhcresu8_icmr_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICMR%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20trial%20run%20of%20transporting%20onco-pathological%20samples%20by%20drones%20under%20its%20i-Drone%20initiative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ficmr-trial-run-tissue-sample-transported-mid-surgery-for-advanced-pathological-testing-5413484%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20pictures%3A%20Eid%20celebrations%20around%20the%20world%22%2C%22content