m%20MOHELA%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20its%20temporary%2C%20mercurial%2C%20and%20extreme%20nature%2C%20the%20current%20situation%20cannot%20be%20considered%20a%20steady-state%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20additional%20staff%20have%20completed%20training%20and%20begun%20responding%20to%20incoming%20calls%20reducing%20average%20wait%20times%2C%20the%20ongoing%20call%20volume%20and%20call%20wait%20times%20are%20anticipated%20to%20fluctuate%20throughout%20the%20on-ramp%20period%2C%20and%20after%20the%20on-ramp%20period%20ends%20in%20the%20fall%2C%26quot%3B%20MOHELA%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%2012%20month%20on-ramp%20period%20that%20began%20in%20October%20during%20which%20any%20missed%20payments%20will%20not%20be%20actively%20reported%20to%20credit%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20report%20comes%20the%20same%20day%20that%20Warren%20is%20holding%20a%20hearing%20to%20examine%20MOHELA's%20servicing%20practices%2C%20along%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loans-mohela-schumer-warren-sanders-invesigation-debt-cancellation-mismanagement-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanagement%20of%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felizabeth-warren-slams-student-loan-company-mohela-ceo-congress-testimony-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20invited%20MOHELA's%20CEO%20to%20testify%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20declined%20on%20his%20behalf%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bactively%20engaged%20in%20conversations%20with%20the%20Subcommittee%20and%20has%20offered%20its%20cooperation%20in%20addressing%20any%20questions%20and%20concerns%20by%20participating%20in%20a%20series%20of%20bipartisan%20briefings%20on%20the%20identified%20areas%20of%20interest%20about%20student%20loan%20servicing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGi