g-noose%2Farticleshow%2F109199137.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Jailed%20For%20Stealing%20Diary%20Belonging%20To%20Joe%20Biden's%20Daughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20from%20Florida%2C%20United%20States%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20a%20month%20in%20prison%20after%20she%20stole%20the%20diary%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20daughter%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20a%20conservative%20advocacy%20group%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fashley-biden-diary-stolen-sentencing-b2526044.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20US%20district%20judge%20ruled%20that%20the%2041-year-old%20would%20face%20jail%20time%20and%20three%20months%20of%20home%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20stole%20Ashley%20Biden's%20diary%20and%20other%20belongings%20from%20a%20friend's%20Florida%20house%20in%202020.%20The%20President's%20daughter%20had%20kept%20them%20at%20home%20for%20safekeeping.%20Harris%20then%20accepted%20%2420%2C000%20from%20Project%20Veritas%2C%20a%20far-right%20organisation%2C%20for%20selling%20the%20journal.%20In%202022%2C%20she%20entered%20a%20guilty%20plea%20to%20a%20charge%20of%20conspiring%20to%20transfer%20stolen%20goods%20across%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20plea%2C%20Harris%20missed%20many%20sentencing%20sessions.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20she%20expressed%20her%20regret%20to%20the%20court%20and%20said%20she%20was%20busy%20caring%20for%20her%20two%20children.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20I%20am%20above%20the%20law.%20I'm%20a%20survivor%20of%20long-term%20domestic%20abuse%20and%20sexual%20trauma%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2041-year-old%20was%20charged%20along%20with%20Robert%20Kurlander%2C%20who%20helped%20her%20with%20selling%20the%20diary.%20Initially%2C%20the%20two%20attempted%20to%20negotiate%20a%20settlement%20with%20a%20repr