e%20and%20diazepam%2C%20or%20Valium%2C%20that%20contained%20xylazine.%20The%20researchers%20contacted%20all%20toxicology%20laboratories%20in%20the%20UK%20last%20year%20to%20gather%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdoctors-alarmed-by-spread-of-zombie-drug-in-new-york-diabolical-4339376%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Doctors%20Alarmed%20By%20Spread%20Of%20Zombie%20Drug%20In%20New%20York%3A%20%26quot%3BDiabolical%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20looked%20at%20drug-testing%20results%20from%20hauls%20seized%20by%20law%20enforcement.%20Although%20the%20numbers%20found%20were%20small-only%20two%20THC%20vapes%20and%20a%20small%20number%20of%20illegally%20sold%20pills%20out%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20products-the%20experts%20say%20it%20is%20still%20extremely%20concerning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Xylazine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fxylazine-powerful-zombie-drug-known-as-tranq-has-penetrated-uk-market-experts-warn-13111400%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20vets%2C%20xylazine%20is%20a%20commonly%20used%20tranquillizer%2C%20often%20mixed%20with%20ketamine%2C%20to%20sedate%20animals%2C%20including%20horses%2C%20cattle%2C%20and%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20non-opioid%20sedative%2C%20it%20is%20able%20to%20inhibit%20the%20transmission%20of%20brain%20impulses%20to%20the%20central%20nervous%20system.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20it%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20a%20darker%20use%20as%20a%20cutting%20agent%20for%20illegal%20drugs%20such%20as%20heroin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20its%20mixture%20with%20fentanyl%20has%20had%20a%20widespread%20impact%20among%20drug%20users%20in%20American%20cities.%20Such%20is%20the%20concern%20in%20Washington%20about%20its%20spread%20that%20Joe%20Biden's%20