special%20it%20is%20that%20we've%20all%20kept%20in%20touch%20over%20five%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20and%20decided%20we%20were%20overdue%20for%20a%20celebration%2C%26quot%3B%20Elhoffer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20celebrated%20a%2010-year%20reunion%20long%20ago%20and%20we%20did%20a%2040-year%20reunion%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%20even%20bigger%20for%20the%2050.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20attendees%20brought%20in%20old%20photos%20and%20their%20McDonald's%20softball%20jerseys%2C%20Elhoffer%20said.%20They%20ate%20together%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20restaurant's%20current%20workers%2C%20and%20even%20signed%20yearbooks%20they'd%20made%20for%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncluding%20those%20who%20work%20for%20franchises%2C%20McDonald's%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20employers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20says%20that%20one%20in%20eight%20Americans%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20chain.%20Its%20network%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20corporate%20and%20franchise%20restaurants%20globally%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-purpose-and-impact%2Fjobs-inclusion-and-empowerment%2Ftalent-and-benefits.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%202%20million%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20McDonald's%20celebrated%20its%20claim%20that%20over%2012%25%20of%20people%20in%20the%20US%20have%20worked%20at%20the%20fast-food%20giant%20by%20hosting%20a%20lavish%20party%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcdonalds1in8.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighlighting%20notable%20former%20crew%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Michelin-starred%20chefs%2C%20astronauts%2C%20and%20Peloton%20instructors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20yearbook%20made%20by%20former%20McDonald's%20workers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661673213f923f7dab0635d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222420%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20McDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElhoffer%20was%2016%20when%20she%20started%20working%20at%20the%20Hazelwood%20restaurant%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%20Most%20of%20the%20other%20former%20workers%20who%20attended%20the%20reunion%20were%20aged%20between%2016%20and%2019%20when%20they%20started%20there%2C%20with%20many%20continuing%20with%20their%20jobs%20throughout%20high%20school%20and%20while%20attending%20local%20colleges%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20almost%20all%20of%20us%2C%20this%20was%20our%20first%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Elhoffer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20became%20close%20friends%20while%20working%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20Elhoffer%20said%2C%20with%20some%20of%20them%20playing%20on%20the%20restaurant's%20softball%20team.%20She%20said%20%26quot%3Bseveral%26quot%3B%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20herself%20included%20%E2%80%94%20met%20their%20spouses%20while%20working%20at%20McDonald's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20former%20McDonald's%20workers%20gather%20in%20a%20restaurant%20for%20a%20reunion%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661673af16bde8d4ead73ef3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20McDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20such%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20within%20this%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20Elhoffer%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20each%20other's%20school%20dances%2C%20weddings%20and%20parents'%20funerals.%20We%20raised%20our%20children%20together%2C%20celebrated%20holidays%2C%20vacationed%20together%20and%20continued%20for%2050%20years%20to%20enjoy%20strong%20friendships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElhoffer%20said%20that%20she%20started%20her%20career%20at%20McDonald's%20by%20managing%20the%20grill%20area.%20She%20was%20later%20promoted%20to%20second%20assistant%20manager%20in%201978.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20attend%20Hamburger%20University%2C%20McDonald's%20training%20school%2C%20and%20become%20a%20store%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElhoffer%20said%20she%20bought%20her%20first%20restaurant%20in%201991.%20She%20now%20owns%20seven%20McDonald's%20restaurants%20around%20St%20Louis.%20Seven%20of%20the%2019%20people%20at%20the%20reunion%20went%20on%20to%20become%20franchisees%2C%20while%20the%20others%20pursued%20different%20career%20paths%2C%20such%20as%20becoming%20teachers%20and%20accountants%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20table%20decorated%20with%20photos%20of%20former%20McDonald's%20workers%20and%2070s%20items%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661673d91caec1275a6e735b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20McDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20since%20she%20started%20working%20at%20McDonald's%20has%20been%20the%20introduction%20of%20drive-thrus%2C%20Elhoffer%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20when%20she%20first%20started%20at%20the%20chain%2C%20orders%20had%20to%20be%20rung%20up%20by%20hand%2C%20and%20workers%20needed%20to%20manually%20add%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20current%20or%20former%20McDonald's%20worker%20or%20franchisee%20with%20a%20story%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20gdean%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-mcdonalds-workers-reunion-restaurant-missouri-class-of-1975-jobs-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712749918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616743e3f923f7dab0635fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-mcdonalds-workers-reu