ust%20contains%20silicon%20dioxide%20which%20when%20inhaled%20over%20some%20time%20leads%20to%20silicosis%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20noticing%20that%20our%20mother%20would%20cough%20a%20lot%20and%20often%20complained%20about%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20breathing.%20Day%20by%20day%2C%20she%20also%20started%20losing%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20four%20years%20until%20one%20day%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20we%20heard%20about%20the%20disease.%20We%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20we%20were%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20how%20long%20she%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20with%20us.%20I%20was%2014%20years%20old%20then%2C%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20she%20would%20be%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20Laxmi%E2%80%99s%20mother%20could%20not%20be%20saved.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20just%2033.%20All%20this%20pain%20was%20for%20Rs%2080-100%20wage%20per%20day.%20If%20I%20had%20known%20about%20the%20consequences%2C%20I%20would%20have%20never%20let%20my%20mother%20go%20to%20that%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laxmi%2C%20now%2028%2C%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvati%20was%20survived%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20her%20daughter%20Laxmi%2C%20and%20two%20younger%20sons.%20That%20day%2C%20Laxmi%20pledged%20to%20escape%20the%20life%20of%20drudgery%20%E2%80%94%20far%20from%20the%20ramming%20mass%20industry%20due%20to%20which%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20silicosis%20patients%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Laxmi%20works%20as%20a%20nursing%20officer%20and%20bears%20all%20the%20household%20responsibilities%20along%20with%20the%20college%20fees%20of%20her%20younger%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20became%20possible%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Samit%20Carr%20sir.%20Firstly%2C%20his%20organisation%20bore%20our%20mother%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20cost%20of%20Rs%203.6%20lakh.%20Then%2C%20he%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20nursing%20by%20getting%20a%20BSc%20degree.%20He%20also%20fought%20to%20get%20us%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20from%20the%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Laxmi%2C%20the%20Jharkhand-based%20non-profit%2C%20Occupational%20Safety%20And%20Health%20Association%20of%20Jharkhand%20(OSHAJ)%2C%20led%20by%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%2C%20has%20helped%20at%20least%2050%20kin%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20get%20compensation%