nk%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20that%20Ukrainian%20first-person%20view%20(FPV)%20drones%20were%20responsible%20for%20two-thirds%20of%20recent%20Russian%20tank%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20success%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20its%20heavy%20reliance%20on%20drones%20reflects%20its%20lack%20of%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20experiencing%20ongoing%20shortages%20in%20artillery%20rounds%20and%20other%20weapons%20that%20are%20usually%20used%20to%20target%20armored%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20up%20for%20this%2C%20it%20has%20used%20FPV%20drones%20for%20a%20range%20of%20tasks%20during%20the%20war%2C%20including%20surveillance%20and%20attacks%20on%20enemy%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20drones%20are%20fitted%20with%20explosives%20and%20are%20remotely%20controlled%20via%20a%20video%20screen%20by%20soldiers%2C%20who%20fly%20them%20into%20Russian%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20troops%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-armored-vehicles-lack-jamming-tech-vulnerable-ukraine-drones-nyt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia's%20electronic%20warfare%20units%2C%20which%20remotely%20scramble%20the%20signals%20used%20to%20control%20drones%2C%20have%20had%20only%20limited%20success%20in%20countering%20their%20use%20against%20tanks%20and%20armored%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20drones%20is%20so%20important%20for%20Ukraine%20that%20it's%20massively%20ramping%20up%20production%20of%20them%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20Strategic%20Industries%2C%20Minister%20Oleksandr%20Kamyshin%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkyivindependent.com%2Fminister-ukraine-to-produce-tens-of-thousands-of-drones-per-month-by-years-end%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20year%20saying%20that%20it%20%3C%2Fa%3Eaimed%20to%20produce%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20the%20devices%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20downsides.%20The%20drones%20are%20no%20replacement%20for%20the%20artillery%20shells%20and%20other%20ammunition%20Ukraine%20is%20desperately%20short%20of%20as%20Republicans%20in%20Congress%20continue%20to%20block%20a%20%2460%20billion%20aid%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20produce%20a%20lot%20of%20drones%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20an%20alternative%20to%20any%20kind%20of%20weapon%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20Axel%20Springer%20media%20outlets%20published%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20proving%20ourselves%20with%20drones%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20increased%20production%20helps%20us%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20is%20not%20a%20substitute%20for%20air%20defense%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20substitute%20for%20long-range%20weapons%2C%20missiles%2C%20long-range%20artillery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFPV%20drones%20have%20a%20relatively%20short%20range%20of%20around%20six%20miles%2C%20while%20missiles%20and%20artillery%20can%20strike%20targets%20accurately%20from%20a%20much%20greater%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Lee%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20in%20the%20Foreign%20Policy%20Research%20Institute's%20Eurasia%20program%2C%20told%20Foreign%20Policy%20the%20drones%20are%20accurate%20only%20around%20half%20the%20time%2C%20and%20an%20experienced%20drone%20operator%20would%20need%20to%20use%20waves%20of%20drone%20attacks%20to%20take%20out%20a%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20usually%20don't%20kill%20a%20tank%20the%20first%20few%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20take%2010%20or%20more%20%5BFPV%20drones%5D%20to%20kill%20a%20tank.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-russia-tank-losses-reflects-shortages-artillery-report-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%