C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century.%20He%20was%20elected%20as%20MP%20in%201999%20from%20present-day%20Theni%20(which%20was%20Periyakulam%20before%20delimitation)%2C%20though%20he%20lost%20from%20here%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Then%2C%20he%20was%20the%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20late%20J.%20Jayalalithaa.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famma-makkal-munnetra-kazhagam-ammk%5C%22%3EAmma%20Makkal%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AMMK)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20has%20hitched%20his%20wagon%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20after%20having%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-seals-seat-sharing-deal-with-allies-for-lok-sabha-elections-5278276%5C%22%3EAIADMK%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOld%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitted%20against%20Dhinakaran%20is%20Thanga%20Tamilselvan%20of%20the%20DMK.%20Both%20used%20to%20be%20in%20the%20AIADMK%20once%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Dhinakaran%20who%20had%20introduced%20Tamilselvan%20to%20Jayalalithaa%20and%20aunt%20Sasikala%2C%20who%20controlled%20the%20party%20apparatus%20back%20then.%20In%202001%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20ticket%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20Andipatti%20assembly%20seat.%20Tamilselvan%20endeared%20himself%20to%20Jayalalithaa%20when%20he%20resigned%20as%20Andipatti%20legislator%20a%20year%20later%20to%20make%20way%20for%20the%20AIADMK%20supremo%20in%20a%20bypoll.%20This%20was%20after%20Jayalalithaa%20was%20cleared%20of%20charges%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20in%20December%202001%20and%20needed%20to%20become%20an%20MLA%20to%20remain%20chief%20minister.%20After%20a%20stint%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Tamilselvan%20returned%20to%20represent%20Andipatti%20in%202011%20and%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhinakaran%20and%20Tamilselvan%20had%20been%20together%20till%20not%20so%20long%20ago.%20After%20Jayalalithaa's%20death%20in%20December%202016%2C%20Tamilselvan%20stood%20with%20Dhinakaran%20and%20contested%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Theni%20as%20a%20candidate%20of%20the%20AMMK%2C%20the%20party%20floated%20by%20the%20latter.%20He%20finished%20third%20behind%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20the%20friends-turned-foes%20match%20up%20against%20each%20other%20today%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Works%20-%20And%20Doesn't%20-%20For%20Dhinakaran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhinakaran%20is%20being%20called%20an%20%60outsider'%20by%20his%20political%20opponents%20but%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20foremost%20leader%20among%20the%20Mukulathor%20or%20Thevars%2C%20the%20community%20that%20dominates%20this%20belt.%20Traditional%20AIADMK%20supporters%20are%20angry%20that%20Edappadi%20Palaniswami%20has%20turned%20the%20party%20from%20a%20Thevar-dominated%20organisation%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20to%20a%20Gounder%20party%2C%20the%20community%20Edappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami%20hails%20from.%20The%20party%20no%20longer%20has%20space%20for%20Thevar%20leaders%20like%20Dhinakaran%2C%20V.K.%20Sasikala%20and%20O.%20Panneerselvam%20(OPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhinakaran%20also%20has%20the%20reputation%20of%20being%20generous%20with%20donations%20to%20temples%20and%20community%20buildings%20like%20schools.%20These%20are%20gestures%20that%20matter%20because%2C%20come%20election%20time%2C%20these%20become%20IOUs.%20Dhinakaran%20is%20also%20using%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20card%20to%20the%20hilt%2C%20talking%20of%20goodies%20that%20could%20come%20the%20constituency's%20way%20should%20it%20elect%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheni%2C%20incidentally%2C%20was%20the%20only%20seat%20the%20NDA%20could%20bag%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%202019.%20P.%20Raveendranath%2C%20son%20of%20O.%20Panneerselvam%2C%20was%20the%20winning%20candidate.%20The%20father-son%20duo%20is%20backing%20Dhinakaran%20this%20time.%20OPS%2C%20as%20the%20story%20goes%2C%20was%20introduced%20to%20Jayalalithaa%20by%20Dhinakaran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20prove%20a%20challenge%20for%20Dhinakaran%20though%20is%20his%20party%20symbol.%20He%20has%20to%20not%20only%20ensure%20that%20the%2015%20lakh%20voters%20in%20Theni%20constituency%20recognise%20his%20pressure%20cooker%20symbol%2C%20but%20he%20also%20knows%20that%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20voter%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sentimental%20attachment%20to%20the%20two%20leaves%20or%20the%20rising%20sun.%20The%20NDA%20is%20banking%20on%20Dhinakaran%20to%20plug%20all%20gaps%2C%20particularly%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20voters%20at%20the%20booth%20level%2C%20given%20his%20experience%20of%20having%20supervised%20several%20elections%20during%20his%20AIADMK%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETamilselvan's%20Strengths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Tamilselvan%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20powerful%20DMK%20machinery%20and%20the%20benefit%20of%20easy%20identification%20with%20the%20rising%20sun%20symbol.%20He%20can%20also%20evoke%20sympathy%20for%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20last%20election.%20Like%20Dhinakaran%2C%20Tamilsevan%2C%20too%2C%20is%20from%20the%20Mukulathor%20community%20and%20has%20handled%20several%20elections.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20managed%20the%20Andipatti%20constituency%20for%20Jayalalithaa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dark%20horse%20would%20be%20the%20AIADMK.%20What%20would%20work%20to%20the%20advantage%20of%20V.T.%20Narayanasamy%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20candidate%2C%20is%20that%20the%20two-leaf%20symbol%20is%20undeniably%20the%20most%20popular%20in%20this%20constituency%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20an%20AIADMK%20stronghold.%20Many%20party%20loyalists%20may%20blindly%20opt%20for%20it%20without%20doing%20a%20micro-analysis%20of%20the%20credentials%20of%20any%20of%20the%20candidates.%20Besides%2C%20Naray