3Cfigcaption%3EPinakothek%20der%20Moderne%20on%20February%2010%2C%202020%2C%20in%20Munich%2C%20Germany.%3Cp%3EHannes%20Magerstaedt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20technician%20at%20a%20German%20museum%20was%20fired%20for%20smuggling%20his%20own%20painting%20into%20one%20of%20its%20galleries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20worker%20hoped%20that%20displaying%20his%20piece%20there%20would%20bring%20him%20an%20'artistic%20breakthrough.'%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20art%20world%20is%20hard%20to%20break%20into%2C%20often%20requiring%20skill%2C%20connections%2C%20and%20name%20recognition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-think-taking-kids-to-see-art-is-so-important-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20museum%3C%2Fa%3E%20worker%20in%20Germany%20was%20fired%20after%20he%20smuggled%20in%20one%20of%20his%20own%20paintings%20and%20hung%20it%20up%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sueddeutsche.de%2Fmuenchen%2Fmuenchen-pinakothek-der-moderne-mitarbeiter-eigenes-bild-1.6532007%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%C3%BCddeutsche%20Zeitung%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20employee%2C%20a%2051-year-old%20man%2C%20worked%20as%20a%20technician%20at%20the%20Pinakothek%20der%20Moderne%20in%20Munich%20but%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-build-side-hustle-etsy-artist-hbo-succession-trader-joes-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoonlighted%20as%20a%20freelance%20artist.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pinakothek%20der%20Moderne%20contains%20works%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalt-disney-salvador-dali-friendship-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalvador%20Dal%C3%AD%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Henri%20Matisse%2C%20which%20can%20sell%20for%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoli