ed%20up%20petitioner%20Sandeep%20Kumar%2C%20a%20former%20AAP%20MLA%20who%20sought%20the%20removal%20of%20Kerjiwal%20from%20the%20office%2C%20for%20trying%20to%20involve%20the%20court%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20thicket%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20will%20impose%20costs%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20like%20a%20James%20Bond%20movie%20where%20we%20will%20have%20sequels.%20(Lt)%20Governor%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20this.%20You%20are%20trying%20to%20involve%20us%20in%20a%20political%20thicket%2C%20that's%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Manmeet%20PS%20Arora%2C%20reiterated%20that%20it%20cannot%20impose%20governor's%20rule%20in%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20petitioner%20was%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20system%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRs%2050%2C000%20costs%20on%20you.%20We%20will%20pass%20the%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2028%2C%20the%20court%20had%20dismissed%20a%20PIL%20for%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20removal%2C%20saying%20that%20while%20the%20petitioner%20had%20failed%20to%20show%20any%20legal%20bar%20that%20prohibited%20the%20arrested%20chief%20minister%20from%20holding%20office%2C%20there%20was%20also%20no%20scope%20for%20judicial%20interference%20in%20such%20cases%20as%20it%20was%20for%20the%20other%20organs%20of%20the%20State%20to%20look%20into%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20it%20cannot%20declare%20a%20breakdown%20of%20the%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%204%2C%20the%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20second%20PIL%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20said%20it%20was%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20choice%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20granted%20liberty%20to%20the%20petitioner%20to%20approach%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20(LG).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar's%20counsel%20argued%20that%20his%20case%20required%20interpretation%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20that%20on%20account%20of%20his%20arrest%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20now%20not%20qualified%20to%20hold%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Manmohan%20said%20if%20there%20was%20a%20grievance%2C%20an%20appeal%20should%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20earlier%20decisions%20instead%20of%20filing%20a%20third%20petition%20on%20the%20same%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20petitioner's%20lawyer%20continued%20to%20argue%20and%20questioned%20where%20he%20must%20go%20if%20the%20government%20was%20not%20according%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20court%20told%20him%20not%20to%20make%20political%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20don't%20give%20a%20political%20speech%20here.%20Go%20to%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20street%20and%20do%20it%20over%20there.%20Please%20don't%20do%20that.%20Your%20client%20may%20be%20a%20politician%20and%20he%20may%20like%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20politics%20but%20we%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20politics.%20We%20stay%20out%20of%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Manmohan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20system.%20Don't%20reduce%20us%20to%20a%20joke.%20It%20is%20only%20because%20of%20people%20like%20you%2C%20your%20client%2C%20that%20we%20are%20reduced%20to%20a%20joke.%20We%20are%20imposing%20some%20heavy%20costs%20on%20you.%20Please%20don't%20come%20back%20with%20repeat%20litigation%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20said%20the%20petitioner%20was%20%26quot%3Bpersisting%26quot%3B%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20a%20single%20judge%20while%20dealing%20with%20his%20petition%20earlier%20this%20week%20and%20said%20imposition%20of%20costs%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20care%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20petitions%20that%20are%20coming%20up%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bdaily%20basis%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20enough.%20Look%20at%20the%20court.%20The%20court%20is%20packed%20with%20litigants.%20Have%20some%20courtesy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20petition%20was%20listed%20before%20the%20acting%20chief%20justice's%20bench%20after%20it%20was%20transferred%20to%20it%20from%20Justice%20Subramonium%20Prasad's%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20dealing%20with%20the%20petition%20on%20April%208%2C%20Justice%20Prasad%20had%20said%20it%20was%20filed%20for%20%26quot%3Bpublicity%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20costs%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20imposed%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20said%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money-laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20now-scrapped%20excise%20policy%20for%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20convener%20incurred%20an%20%26quot%3Bincapacity%26quot%3B%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20chief%20minister's%20functions%20under%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20March%2021%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20high%20court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection%20from%20coercive%20action%20by%20the%20federal%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20had%20said%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20%26quot%3Bunavailability%26quot%3B%20complicates%20the%20constitutional%20mechanism%20and%20he%20can%20never%20function%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20from%20prison%20according%20to%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndica