%20heart%20of%20the%20subcontinent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hearing%20Aid%20Employs%20Tech%20Used%20in%20US%20Army%20Helmets%20To%20Help%20Thousands%20Hear%3B%20Has%20Rs%205.5%20Crore%20in%20Revenues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20final%20year%20of%20studying%20robotics%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20communication%20engineering%2C%20Kanishka%20Patel%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20news%20article%20that%20would%20shape%20his%20future.%20The%20piece%20detailed%20a%20groundbreaking%20development%20by%20the%20British%20defence%20and%20security%20firm%20BAE%20Systems%20%E2%80%94%20an%20army%20helmet%20using%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20to%20facilitate%20communication%20among%20soldiers%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%2C%20Kanishka%20delved%20into%20research%20on%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20and%20its%20potential%20applications.%20If%20it%20could%20enhance%20communication%20amidst%20the%20cacophony%20of%20warfare%2C%20he%20pondered%2C%20what%20other%20transformative%20uses%20could%20it%20serve%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMight%20it%20offer%20hope%20to%20those%20dealing%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283166%2Fuber-india-sahib-echoes-cafe-delhi-inspiring-indians%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20individuals%20with%20conditions%20like%20microtia%2C%20whose%20external%20ears%20are%20underdeveloped%3F%20Could%20this%20technology%20present%20a%20non-surgical%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20for%20millions%20worldwide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%E2%80%99s%20mind%20buzzed%20with%20possibilities%2C%20igniting%20a%20passion%20to%20explore%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20this%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20resounding%20affirmation%20of%20their%20journey%2C%20Kani