al%20trait%20in%20combating%20food%20security%20threats%20posed%20by%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neelam%2C%20now%2037%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20sadly%2C%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20adoption%20of%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20are%20abandoning%20heirloom%20varieties.%20This%2C%20coupled%20with%20frequent%20floods%2C%20has%20made%20agriculture%20unsustainable%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20preserving%20these%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20which%20serve%20as%20an%20essential%20resource%20for%20farmers%