c%20seed%20varieties%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20some%20were%20accessible%20for%20rice%2C%20none%20were%20available%20for%20vegetables.%20The%20absence%20of%20reserves%20or%20authenticity%20in%20seed%20sources%20was%20concerning.%20Instead%2C%20the%20market%20was%20saturated%20with%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20worrying%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20also%20observed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20were%20switching%20to%20hybrid%20seeds%20and%20overlooked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315599%2Fhyderabad-chandana-naveen-gade-seedbasket-agro-services-sell-native-seeds-to-urban-gardeners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheirloom%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20only%20hybrid%20seeds%20were%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20the%20market%20to%20the%20farmers.%20This%20was%20never%20a%20solution%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98evergreen%E2%80%99%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20hybrid%20seeds%20offer%20higher%20yields%20in%20one%20season%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20saved%20for%20the%20following%20year.%20Consequently%2C%20farmers%20neglected%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20their%20sovereignty%20over%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%20Since%20then%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20been%20to%20conserve%20decade-old%20seeds%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20the%20traditional%20wisdom%20imparted%20by%20his%20father%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20set%20out%20in%20search%20of%20these%20heirloom%20treasures.%20In%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Neelam%20has%20conserved%20nearly%20800%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20capsicum%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20200%20%3Ca%20