%5C%22%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20difference%20between%20hybrid%20and%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20hybrid%20varieties%20give%20more%20yield%2C%20they%20are%20produced%20via%20genetic%20manipulation.%20We%20compel%20hybrid%20seeds%20to%20grow%20using%20external%20fertilisers%20and%20chemicals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Haryana%20are%20extremely%20dependent%20on%20these%20outside%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20further%20points%20out%20that%2C%20unlike%20heirloom%20varieties%2C%20the%20seed%20saved%20from%20hybrids%20does%20not%20grow%20true%20to%20its%20type%20in%20the%20next%20cycle.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20be%20less%20vigorous%20and%20more%20genetically%20variable.%20If%20you%20cannot%20replicate%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20keeping%20the%20seeds.%20It%20only%20compels%20farmers%20to%20buy%20new%20seeds%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%20As%20they%20are%20open-pollinated%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20replicate%20those%20seeds%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20produce%20harvested%20from%20both%20varieties%20differ%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20tomatoes%20are%20available%20year-round%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%20when%20we%20only%20had%20them%20in%20winter.%20To%20satisfy%20demand%2C%20farmers%20now%20grow%20tomatoes%20in%20mountainous%20areas%20with%20heavy%20fertiliser%20use.%20However%2C%20organically%20grown%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20respective%20seasons%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20but%20are%20richer%20in%20nutrients%2C%20tastier%2C%20and%20more%20vibrant%20in%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20France%2C%20various%20tomato%20varieties%20were%20once%20used%20in%20different%20recipes%2C%20but%20now%20a%20single%2C%20sweeter%20tomato%20is%20used%20universally%2C%20replacing%20the%20sour%20ones%20of%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346321%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point%20doing%20all%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20work%20received%20a%20great%20response%20from%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20going%20beyond%20conserving%20seeds%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Neelam%20now%20trains%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20in%20seed%20conservation.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%94%20including%20states%20like%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20them%20grow%20and%20conserve%20their%20own%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20Neelam%20sells%20approximately%208%2C000%20packets%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20at%20Rs%2099%20each%20to%20farmers.%20With%20these%20seeds%20and%20the%20training%20he%20provides%2C%20farmers%20can%20cultivate%20crops%20and%20harvest%20new%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%20ensuring%20sustainable%20food%20security%20%E2%80%94%20a%20goal%20Neelam%20passionately%20pursues%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Diganata%20Bora%20has%20been%20cultivating%20vegetables%20using%20such%20heirloom%20seeds%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20in%20Paschim%20Manjiri%20village%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20hybrid%20varieties%2C%20we%20get%20good%20yield%20using%20heirloom%20ones.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B0.33%20acre%5D%2C%20we%20now%20get%206-7%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20over%202-2.5%20quintals.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20input%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20as%20we%20use%20readily%20available%20cow%20dung%20as%20fertiliser.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20switch%3B%20now%20our%20soil%20fertility%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diganata%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20when%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b