20praying%20to%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20little%2C%20I%20lost%20my%20dad.%20My%20mother%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20milk%20anymore.%20But%2C%20when%20she%20came%20to%20return%20the%20coupons%20to%20your%20great-grandfather%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20supply%20milk%20to%20the%20family%20until%20her%20children%20grew%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20woman%20had%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20sweet%20formula%20for%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20looking%20to%20stop%20by%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%2C%20Sarfaraz%20recommends%20you%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331511%2Fstory-behind-kuremal-mohanlal-kulfi-iconic-brand-old-delhi-haryana-farmer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etry%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulfis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20Indian%20ice%20cream).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20always%20ring%20a%20bell%20with%20me.%20The%20cool%20creamy%20and%20mouthwatering%20taste%20is%20amazing.%20It%20melts%20in%20the%20plate%20and%20even%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebasundi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(thickened%20milk)%20that%20comes%20up%20is%20just%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revamped%20Parsi%20dairy%20Farm%20also%20boasts%20a%20%E2%80%98Great%20Indian%20Toffee%20Wonderland%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20has%20an%20array%20of%20delicious%20sweets%20(earlier%20known%20as%20milk%20drops).%20Growing%20up%20these%20were%20Bakhtyar%E2%80%99s%20favourites%20and%20now%20he%20enjoys%20the%20fudge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20family%20prides%20themselves%20on%20their%20legacy%2C%20they%20mention%20their%20mothers%20who%20were%20founding%20pillars%20of%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20took%20the%20reigns%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20common%20for%20women%20to%20work.%20Our%20fathers%20also%20were%20extremely%20supportive%20of%20them%20doing%20this%3B%20encouraging%20them%20and%20helping%