%2C%20P%20Saravanan%E2%80%99s%20turmeric%20crop%20was%20destroyed%20due%20to%20disease.%20This%20was%20the%20proverbial%C2%A0%20wake%20up%20call%20for%20the%2058-year-old%20farmer%2C%20which%20prompted%20his%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20farming%20family%2C%20Saravanan%20realised%20that%20all%20he%20had%20to%20do%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensure%20a%20good%20crop%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20benefitted%20him%20as%20well%20as%20the%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20was%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20grandparents%E2%80%99%20style%20of%20farming%20and%20abandon%20chemicals%20and%20pesticides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Namakkal%20resident%20soon%20realised%20the%20benefits%20of%20organic%20farming%2C%20and%20through%20different%20training%20at%20the%20local%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20along%20with%20his%20innovations%20and%20home%20recipes%20to%20keep%20pests%20at%20bay%2C%20Saravanan%20soon%20became%20a%20certified%20organic%20farmer%20with%20many%20awards%20up%20his%20sleeve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20he%20has%20been%20practising%20integrated%20farming%20for%20several%20decades%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitiated%20with%20avoiding%20chemicals%20completely%2C%20he%20soon%20moved%20towards%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20vermicompost%2C%20a%20biogas%20unit%20and%20hydroponics.%20Unable%20to%20cultivate%20enough%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle%2C%20hydroponic%20maize%20production%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20gamechanger%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20he%20has%20been%20using%20this%20method%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%20his%20livestock.%20What%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20it%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20grows%20it%20in%20his%20cupboard!%20He%20uses%20the%